- Request (application/json)

    - Attributes (object)

        - `invitation` (object)
            - `emails` (array[email])
            - `user_ids` (array[uuid])
            - `role_ids` (object)
                - *271A3A83-EA0C-450D-BAFB-51ED42C4CF10 (uuid)* (id) - Map from email / user ID to Space Role ID
