                - `user_ids` (object)
                    - *2d6696ad-f8ec-42a2-80c4-1ebd8196ce9c (uuid)* (object) - an object indexed by User UUIDs
                        - Invitee (InviterInvitee)
            - `errors` (object)
                - `emails`
                    - *user@example.com (email)* (array[string]) - Array of error strings indexed by Email
